## Registration
To start the registration process or to log in, visit https://product.sustainabilitytool.com/ 

Anyone can register your organisation at no cost. This opens up the ability to measure and report the carbon footprint of your products and assets, and to share this information with your clients.

Each individual within your organisation will have their own login, allowing for a personalised experience. Users can be part of one or several company accounts, making it possible to manage multiple portfolios conveniently.

For existing users of any of the Sustainability Tool suite of products, your rom the Sustainability Tool suite to access the Product Carbon Calculator.
